107
00:14:29,761 --> 00:14:35,830
If we allow the bias to manifest in our minds and hearts, then we can begin to undermine it.

108
00:14:36,772 --> 00:14:38,274
First, there's the acceptance.

109
00:14:38,293 --> 00:14:39,936
This is a bias in my heart.

110
00:14:40,456 --> 00:14:43,380
And once I accept it, we can recognize it as unwholesome.

111
00:14:44,822 --> 00:14:51,451
Now, usually because it arises because we've seen or heard someone whom the bias hates.

112
00:14:52,172 --> 00:14:56,477
So we can bring that person to mind, see the situation from their point of view.

113
00:14:56,518 --> 00:15:02,125
We can apologize to them as an active drama practice within ourselves.

114
00:15:03,086 --> 00:15:05,850
Then we can hold the person in a caring embrace.

115
00:15:06,336 --> 00:15:08,460
You can't hate and care at the same time.

116
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:13,486
Sometimes you have to be creative with this process of undermining biases.

117
00:15:15,769 --> 00:15:27,044
If we're sitting in meditation and we get one of these biases coming up, you might find it just as useful to just sit with the aversion, just the feeling of the aversion.

118
00:15:28,087 --> 00:15:32,716
And what we're doing, we're just allowing that bad energy to exhaust itself.

119
00:15:33,216 --> 00:15:44,975
And then if we stay to the very end, when that feeling of aversion comes to an end, we stay to the point where it disappears, you might experience it transforming into the opposite.

120
00:15:45,255 --> 00:15:50,745
So you might suddenly find your heart full of love or peacefulness or some other positive state.

121
00:15:51,446 --> 00:15:52,408
Nothing's lost.

122
00:15:52,725 --> 00:15:55,850
in allowing these negative states to come up and pass away.

123
00:15:55,870 --> 00:15:59,395
They're always changing towards their opposites.

124
00:15:59,416 --> 00:16:15,000
This we find in the right attitude of the Eightfold Path, which is stated as going from greed to generosity, hatred to love, and cruelty to compassion.

125
00:16:15,019 --> 00:16:21,669
